The '''Morokodo''' are an ethnic group numbering over 40,000 people living in the [[South Sudan]]ese state of [[Central Equatoria]].<ref>[http://www.gurtong.org/resourcecenter/people/profile_tribe.asp?TribeID=122 Gurtong Peace Project]</ref> They speak [[Morokodo language]], a [[Nilo-Saharan language]]. 

